{"word":"Nebo","slug":"nebo","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Nebo</b> <a href=\"#/H5015\">H5015</a> <br/> 1. A city allotted to Reuben:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=32&verse=3'>Num 32:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=32&verse=38'>Num 32:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=8'>1Ch 5:8</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=15&verse=2'>Isa 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=1'>Jer 48:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=22'>Jer 48:22</a> <br/> 2. A mountain range east of the Jordan:<br/> - Moses views Canaan from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=50'>Deu 32:50</a> <br/> - Moses dies on<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=34&verse=1'>Deu 34:1</a> <br/> 3. A city in Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=29'>Ezr 2:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=33'>Neh 7:33</a><br/> 4. The ancestor of certain Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=43'>Ezr 10:43</a><br/> 5. A Babylonian idol<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=46&verse=1'>Isa 46:1</a>"}]}